headline: Vera Bradley (VRA) Reports Q1 Loss, Lags Revenue Estimates
summary: Vera Bradley (VRA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -176.92% and 4.21%, respectively, for the quarter ended April 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
